hwt.bodyText:
If((clk)._onRisingEdge(),
    If(rst_n._eq(0x0),
        state_reg(state_type.fullIdle),
        on_off_reg(0x0),
        lenRem_reg(33.auto_cast(Bits(7))),
        baseAddr_reg(0x0),
    ).Else(
        state_reg(state_reg_next),
        on_off_reg(on_off_reg_next),
        lenRem_reg(lenRem_reg_next),
        baseAddr_reg(baseAddr_reg_next),
    ),
)
